quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  27,15,"Ni$ Nefka tamusni i Dawed akked Sliman. Nnan: \"ccekôan i Öebbi, i a$ Ismenyafen i waîaû n yimdanen iumnen"
  27,16,"Sliman iwôet Dawed, u inna: \"a yimdanen! Nepwaselmed tutlayt n yifôax; ippunefk a$ si yal cci. Ayagi, s tidep, ard lfevl n ûûeê"
  27,17,"Pwajemmlen d, i Sliman, i²âsekôiwen is si leonun, imdanen, ifôax. Mdarraren"
  27,18,"Armi, mi bbwven ar te$zut n twevfin, tenna d tweîuft: \"a yaweîîuf, kecmemt ar ixxamen nnkwent, mulac, war ccekk, a kwent iéd Sliman, neppa akked iâsekôiwen is, ur faqen"
  27,19,"Icmumeê, ivûa, $ef wayen d tenna. Inna: \"a Mass iw! Err iyi ad snemmre$ l$it iK, is i $ T$atev, nek akked imawlan iw; ad xedme$ ise$ ara Tôaviv; Ssekcem iyi, s uêunu K, ar imdanen iK imaânen"
  27,20,"Issefqed ifôax, inna: \"acimi ur wala$ ara iççibib, day d l$ayeb"
  27,21,"War ccekk, ad sâaddi$ fellas aâaqeb uqsiê, ne$ a t zlu$, ne$ a d iawi tasebbiwt tubrizt"
  27,22,"Ur iâaîîel ara. Inna d: \"fehme$ ayen ur tefhimev. Usi$ d $uôek si Saba, s usali unûiê"
  27,23,"Ih, ufi$ en tameîîut d tagelliî nnsen. Ippunefk as si yal cci. £uôes asgeld abarar"
  27,24,"Ufi$ p in, neppat akked ugdud is, la kennun i yiîij, war Öebbi. Cciîan icebbeê asen igiten nnsen. Iveôf iten seg ubrid, d$a nitni ur pwanhan"
  27,25,"Acimi ur knan ara i Öebbi, id Issufu$en lesrar, di tmurt akked igenwan, i Iéôan ayen teppeffrem u ayen d tepberriêem"
  27,26,"Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"
  27,27,"Inna: \"a néeô ma tessawlev d tidep, ne$ ma keçç seg ikeddaben"
  27,28,"Öuê s tebôap iw agi, veggeô asen p, sinna, wexxeô asen, wali acu ara d rren"
  27,29,"Tenna: \"a yimvebbôen, tepwaveggeô iyi d tebôap tukyist"
  27,30,"Ih, s$uô Sliman. Apan: s yisem n Öebbi Aênin Ipêunun"
  27,31,"Ur ssem$waôet ara iman nnwen $uôi, aset ed $uôi, d imvuâen"